Name: Very Cavallari
Title: Shake Ya Palm Palms
Desc: Kristin heads to Palm Springs, Calif., for a campaign shoot; Brittainy has a shipping issue.
LongDescription: Kristin balances business and pleasure as she heads to Palm Springs, Calif., for a campaign shoot; in Nashville, Brittainy struggles to take control over a massive shipping issue; Jay has a hard time with Kristin always being out of town.
